OL,3,CRapist who called victim 'scum' and
OL,4,C'dog' jailed for 19 years
OL,6,FAn "abhorrent" man who sexually abused
OL,7,Fa teenager and raped her as a woman
OL,8,Fhas been handed a 19-year prison
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FLee Sharp restrained his victim, spat
OL,12,Fin her face and repeatedly referred to
OL,13,Fher as things like "scum of the earth"
OL,14,Fsaying nobody would want her.
OL,16,FOn one occasion he sent her a message
OL,17,Fsaying "you dog, you're going to die
OL,18,Ffor this".
