OL,6,FSharp, who is 42 and of Easterly
OL,7,FTerrace, Sticklepath, was found guilty
OL,8,Fof sexual activity with a child,
OL,9,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour and
OL,10,Frape following a trial in August 2024.
OL,12,FHe was handed a 19-year prison term
OL,13,Ffollowing a sentencing hearing at
OL,14,FExeter Crown Court on Monday 30
OL,15,FOctober.
OL,17,FThe judge also sentenced him to six
OL,18,Fyears on extended licence and granted
OL,19,Fa restraining order.
