OL,6,FThe court heard that Sharp had
OL,7,Fsexually abused the woman when she was
OL,8,Fa teenager `knowing that she was under
OL,9,Fthe age of consent ` and had told her
OL,10,Fto keep quiet about what had happened.
OL,12,FSharp also raped the woman as an
OL,13,Fadult, and was physically and
OL,14,Femotionally abusive towards her, the
OL,15,Fcourt was told.
OL,17,FAbusive messages that Sharp had sent
OL,18,Fto her were shown in evidence.
