OL,6,FSharp denied the offences throughout
OL,7,Fthe court process but was found guilty
OL,8,Fby a jury.
OL,10,FInvestigating officer for Devon and
OL,11,FCornwall Police, Sergeant Tina Dalton,
OL,12,Fthanked the woman for the courage she
OL,13,Fshowed working with police to bring
OL,14,FSharp to justice.
OL,16,F"Sharp abused her repeatedly and
OL,17,Fbehaved in an abhorrent way," she said.
