OL,6,FShe added: "I hope that the outcome
OL,7,Ftoday will give others, who may have
OL,8,Fbeen victims of these types of crimes,
OL,9,Fthe confidence to come forward and
OL,10,Freport it.
OL,12,F"No matter what time has passed, or
OL,13,Fthe circumstances, we will listen, and
OL,14,Fyou will be heard."
